      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should ask my doctor but i cant get an appointment for like two weeks and i'm already exhausted. it's just melatonin, right? it's a natural supplement. i feel like it won't really interfere with the ambien, it should just help it kick in faster so i don't spend hours staring at the ceiling. isnt it basically safe since they both just help with sleep?",
